What is a more conservative value?

00:29:08.830 --> 00:29:13.499
Higher GDP
growth or balanced budget?

00:29:13.499 --> 00:29:18.909
Because here you have a
choice.

00:29:18.909 --> 00:29:27.149
You can either be growing towards balanced
budget, or you can be stimulating your GDP.

00:29:27.149 --> 00:29:30.149
What is
more conservative, and what is more populist

00:29:30.149 --> 00:29:33.610
, and what is more leftist and what is trying
to please all?

