Over consumption.

00:31:28.970 --> 00:31:33.350
How are we going
to get out of it?

00:31:33.350 --> 00:31:35.400
By consuming even more.

00:31:35.400 --> 00:31:40.220
And, you
know, Obama gets blamed by many economists,

00:31:40.220 --> 00:31:44.110
oh, you're
not inducing the economy to spend, and this

00:31:44.110 --> 00:31:46.249
is the
debate that we have in Europe as well.

00:31:46.249 --> 00:31:49.499
We have to run
fiscal deficits to get everything moving.

00:31:49.499 --> 00:31:53.809
So we will
spend our way out of the crisis.

